                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I was on duty at Greenwich fair, in plain clothes, on the 4th of April—I saw the prisoner take this hand<lb></lb>kerchief from the prosecutor's pocket—he attempted to run away, and threw it on the ground—I took him—I had watched him for half an hour</p>
